                     <a id="a059661"></a>
                     <div class="entry" id="entry-59661">
                        <h1 class="entry-header"><a href="http://www.treehugger.com/files/2010/05/sunscreen-dangers-revisited.php">Ask Pablo: Does Sunscreen Cause More Skin Cancer Than It Prevents? (Updated)</a></h1>
                     <h5 class="tagline">by <a href="http://www.treehugger.com/author/pablo-paster-san-francisco-1/">Pablo Paster, San Francisco</a> <a href="http://www.treehugger.com/feeds/authors/pablo.xml"><img style="margin-bottom: -1px;" src="http://www.treehugger.com/images_site/feed-icon-10x10.png" /></a> on  	05.24.10</h5>
                        <div class="entry-content">
                           <div class="entry-body">
                              <div class="cat-indicator">

<a href="http://www.treehugger.com/science_technology/">Science & Technology</a>
<br>

